# UtilityOps documentation

Before changing navigation, state, data flow, or visual design:

1. **`AGENTS.md`** (repo root) — stack, conventions, do-not-do list
2. **`docs/architecture.md`** — current SPA vs target platform
3. **`docs/design-system.md`** — tokens, themes, charts (required for UI)

Product requirements live in **`docs/prd_utilityops_monitoring_system.md`**; do not paste FR IDs into user-visible copy.

After token or theme changes, keep **`docs/design-system.md`** aligned with `src/index.css` and chart code.
